&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&amp;nbsp;are&amp;nbsp;looking&amp;nbsp;for&amp;nbsp;a&amp;nbsp;motivated&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;diligent&amp;nbsp;Accountant&amp;nbsp;to&amp;nbsp;support&amp;nbsp;the&amp;nbsp;growth&amp;nbsp;of&amp;nbsp;our&amp;nbsp;global&amp;nbsp;business&amp;nbsp;activities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform&amp;nbsp;accurate&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;timely&amp;nbsp;general&amp;nbsp;accounting&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;reporting&amp;nbsp;activities,&amp;nbsp;including&amp;nbsp;journal&amp;nbsp;entries,&amp;nbsp;accrual&amp;nbsp;calculations,&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;allocation&amp;nbsp;postings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage&amp;nbsp;monthly,&amp;nbsp;quarterly,&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;annual&amp;nbsp;closing&amp;nbsp;processes,&amp;nbsp;ensuring&amp;nbsp;accuracy&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;adherence&amp;nbsp;to&amp;nbsp;deadlines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure&amp;nbsp;the&amp;nbsp;reliability&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;integrity&amp;nbsp;of&amp;nbsp;financial&amp;nbsp;records&amp;nbsp;in&amp;nbsp;compliance&amp;nbsp;with&amp;nbsp;IFRS&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;applicable&amp;nbsp;local&amp;nbsp;accounting&amp;nbsp;standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist&amp;nbsp;in&amp;nbsp;the&amp;nbsp;preparation&amp;nbsp;of&amp;nbsp;financial&amp;nbsp;statements&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;management&amp;nbsp;reports&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate&amp;nbsp;with&amp;nbsp;external&amp;nbsp;auditors&amp;nbsp;to&amp;nbsp;ensure&amp;nbsp;a&amp;nbsp;smooth&amp;nbsp;audit&amp;nbsp;process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;implement&amp;nbsp;process&amp;nbsp;improvements&amp;nbsp;to&amp;nbsp;enhance&amp;nbsp;efficiency,&amp;nbsp;automation,&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;internal&amp;nbsp;controls&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;Skill Set and Qualifications&lt;/u&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ACCA,&amp;nbsp;ACA,&amp;nbsp;or&amp;nbsp;equivalent&amp;nbsp;professional&amp;nbsp;qualification&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+&amp;nbsp;years&amp;nbsp;of&amp;nbsp;relevant&amp;nbsp;experience&amp;nbsp;in&amp;nbsp;accounting&amp;nbsp;or&amp;nbsp;audit,&amp;nbsp;preferably&amp;nbsp;within&amp;nbsp;a&amp;nbsp;multinational&amp;nbsp;environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong&amp;nbsp;technical&amp;nbsp;knowledge&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;practical&amp;nbsp;application&amp;nbsp;of&amp;nbsp;IFRS&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced&amp;nbsp;proficiency&amp;nbsp;in&amp;nbsp;Excel&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;financial&amp;nbsp;management&amp;nbsp;systems;&amp;nbsp;experience&amp;nbsp;with&amp;nbsp;QuickBooks&amp;nbsp;is&amp;nbsp;an&amp;nbsp;advantage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Results-driven&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;committed&amp;nbsp;to&amp;nbsp;delivering&amp;nbsp;high-quality&amp;nbsp;work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability&amp;nbsp;to&amp;nbsp;work&amp;nbsp;effectively&amp;nbsp;in&amp;nbsp;a&amp;nbsp;fast-paced&amp;nbsp;environment&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;manage&amp;nbsp;multiple&amp;nbsp;priorities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable&amp;nbsp;working&amp;nbsp;in&amp;nbsp;a&amp;nbsp;multicultural&amp;nbsp;setting&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;collaborating&amp;nbsp;with&amp;nbsp;international&amp;nbsp;teams&amp;nbsp;across&amp;nbsp;different&amp;nbsp;time&amp;nbsp;zones&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent&amp;nbsp;written&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;spoken&amp;nbsp;English&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based&amp;nbsp;in&amp;nbsp;Mauritius&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you keen to work in a well-resourced startup environment, where your ideas, experience, and drive to find creative solutions makes a difference? We’d like to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Forteus is the asset management division of the Numeus Group. Forteus offers a suite of liquid, actively managed investment products focused on generating alpha in the digital asset markets. Forteus is backed by Schroders, one of the largest global asset managers.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a dynamic, results-driven professional to lead asset raising across North America. You will develop and execute a strategic plan to engage and build trusted relationships with investors, raise capital for the Forteus product suite, and drive measurable growth for the firm. This is a high-impact role where your ability to connect, influence, and deliver results will be recognized and rewarded.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as Forteus’s chief ambassador to investors in North America&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and manage a pipeline of investors for the Forteus funds across all investor segments, with an initial focus on early adopters, including family offices, HNWI, crypto native investors, and wealth managers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effectively balance near-term asset raising goals with more scalable, institutional relationships over the medium/longer term&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build deep knowledge of Forteus products and digital asset markets, contributing towards investor education of these markets and investment opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate the Forteus “story” and build the Forteus brand, representing Forteus at investor conferences and networking events&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage a robust and well organized sales process, document leads and interactions within the firm’s CRM system, and communicate KPIs and key insights regarding our asset raising and investor pipeline development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skill Set And Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Leadership:&lt;/strong&gt; 10+ years experience in senior client facing / sales roles in the asset management industry (preferably in alternative assets or digital assets).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Network:&lt;/strong&gt; Well-established relationships with institutional investors, family offices, and HNWI investors. Ready access to networks that can accelerate Forteus’s growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sales:&lt;/strong&gt; Exceptional client development, fundraising, and deal-making skills. Proven ability to grow AUM and cultivate trusted relationships with institutional investors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Profile &amp;amp; Credibility:&lt;/strong&gt; Respected industry profile with a history of integrity and excellence. Confident communicator capable of engaging senior stakeholders and decision makers.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Industry Knowledge&lt;/strong&gt;: Proven experience establishing and managing sales processes to institutional standards, along with asset management product development across regulatory frameworks.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Communication:&lt;/strong&gt; Outstanding verbal and written communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Digital Assets:&lt;/strong&gt; Existing knowledge of the digital asset space is preferable; a demonstrable passion to learn and become immersed in the space is essential&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; US based, ideally in our NYC office, although strong candidates in other locations will be considered&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join us and play a defining role in shaping our growth – where your contributions will be visible, rewarded, and instrumental to the firm’s success.&lt;/p&gt;
