&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an experienced DevOps Infrastructure Engineer to manage and maintain our cloud-based systematic trading infrastructure and build tools to enable and accelerate research. The ideal candidate will have extensive experience in software development tools, production management and cloud tooling in a systematic trading environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
