&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Forteus is the asset management division of Numeus Group, a diversified digital asset investment firm built to the highest institutional standards across Alpha Strategies, Trading, and Asset Management. Forteus is backed by Schroders plc, one of Europe’s largest asset managers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our team brings decades of experience across finance, blockchain, and technology. We operate with institutional discipline and an entrepreneurial mindset, combining deep capital markets expertise with a conviction in the long-term significance of blockchain technology and digital assets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an experienced, fundamentally driven discretionary Portfolio Manager to lead a dedicated strategy focused on publicly listed equities with meaningful exposure to the blockchain and digital asset ecosystem. This includes technology providers, infrastructure companies, miners, exchanges, and financial services firms building in the space.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you will define the investment framework, drive stock selection, construct the portfolio, and manage risk. You will work alongside digital asset specialists, traders, and experienced investment professionals to build a differentiated, institutional-quality strategy.&lt;/p&gt;
