&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Manage a discretionary equity portfolio, with full accountability for position sizing, sector exposure, and risk management&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Apply a rigorous bottom-up research process to evaluate publicly listed companies across the blockchain and digital asset ecosystem&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Generate high-conviction long ideas grounded in deep financial analysis, competitive positioning, and management assessment&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Develop clear, defensible investment theses supported by detailed financial modeling and valuation analysis (DCF, comparables, scenario analysis)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Continuously monitor portfolio holdings, industry developments, and evolving market structure to refine positioning&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Produce high-quality investment memos and communicate recommendations clearly to internal stakeholders and clients&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Contribute to broader thematic research at the intersection of digital assets and traditional financial markets&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
