&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5+ years of experience as a discretionary Portfolio Manager or Senior Fundamental Research Analyst within a hedge fund, asset manager, or investment bank, with a demonstrable track record&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Deep expertise in equity financial analysis, valuation, and portfolio construction&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Strong understanding of blockchain technology, digital asset market structure, and how public companies monetize this ecosystem&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Independent thinker with sound judgment and a disciplined investment process&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ability to articulate complex investment ideas clearly and persuasively&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Proficiency in analytical tools such as Python or SQL is advantageous&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fluent English speaker&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
